::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod pulled up infront of the Cybertronian Fire.
"Last stop, all passangers out." He said jokeinly.

::DrillBit::

"Ok, I'll let you rest." He said to KitKat.
He then walked over to a chair, and sat down. He knew she wasn;t telling
him everything, but he didn't want to hound her. But he found himself
constantly looking at her. He decided to stay, and watch over her.
